{"tid":1394751,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"何超蓮不會視罷工為曠工：我尊重唔同聲音","createTime":"2019-08-01T13:54:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-01T14:28:44.000Z","uid":134071,"like":53,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"3a720b02b5d3c2a91884b5f26517c3d7c514fe02","tid":1394751,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T13:54:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190801/59885988\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190801%2F59885988&d=BmTzKXBjX6ru83xd6aIIEbc9MeEcP%2Bid7GYOBZmoUoI%3D&h=18918e71\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190801%2F59885988&h=96a95df6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190801/59885988</a><br />\n<br />\n 2019年08月01日<br />\n【逆權運動】何超蓮不會視罷工為曠工：我尊重唔同聲音 <br />\n<br />\n何超蓮今天在旺角出席慈善活動，現場親手製作多款甜品，超蓮是個超級甜品控，她笑言自己吃甜品是用另一個胃，就算吃飽了也堅持吃甜品，她笑說：「有一次同G.E.M去日本，搵勁多嘢食，由朝食到晚，有啲連訂咗位嘅餐廳都要取消，我哋會用行取代搭車，希望個胃空出位置。」超蓮愛烹飪，尤其是整甜品，經常都親自炮製甜品給家人品嚐，問到男友竇驍有嚐過她的廚藝嗎？超蓮即封口，笑指不回應有關男友的事。提到愛甜品，超蓮表示一直希望開甜品店，她說：「因為我都唔係整得好叻，有諗過讀藍帶課程，但日本冇3個月課程，只得瑞士同澳洲有3個月課程，我冇時間過去，我有一個心願，希望開到甜品舖，因為甜品可以減輕負面情緒，會令人開心番，sharing is caring，要同啲朋友一齊分享。」<br />\n<br />\n提到最近接連的社會運動，超蓮看到不快的新聞後會否吃甜品減壓？她說：「保持心境開朗，食甜品令心情愉快！」超蓮指最近的事亦減少來港旅客，而她在銅鑼灣開設的牛肉麵店也停業數天，問到下周一網民自發舉行「全港大罷工」，超蓮說：「我尊重唔同嘅聲音，如果要發表自己意見，係冇限制，好似噚日打風，11點都叫員工快啲返屋企，點知個風真係超級大風。」至於若有員工參與罷工，超蓮表明不會視為曠工，而暫時亦未有員工請假。<br />\n<br />\n採訪：羅慧敏<br />\n攝影：葉君海"},{"pid":"f86702c8894dd614a6ea028ebd2f51af07d38fff","tid":1394751,"uid":125029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T13:54:54.000Z","msg":"同我瘋狂推爆「公務員事務局」FB Page<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1394653\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1394653</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"40f2c0f8699e3d520aca3e80b18136e7e41f5818","tid":1394751,"uid":244889,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T13:56:04.000Z","msg":"女神<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea709d0d39ad7812eb34fd14323cb71f4b049b43","tid":1394751,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T13:58:28.000Z","msg":"點解咁都會有負評"},{"pid":"f7b9daeb0f6225ae723bcb88557d8ba67695157d","tid":1394751,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T14:08:26.000Z","msg":"何東後人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f5f787009abae869bc4b16d8cdda7bea6f5121d","tid":1394751,"uid":22700,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T14:10:59.000Z","msg":"超蓮係少有既良心富二代"},{"pid":"a20adb7a58f8f64ee59ce5b31f9946ce40c6692d","tid":1394751,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T14:12:50.000Z","msg":"想瘋狂同佢打工<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8833a170aa496727220722554175435ec2b33091","tid":1394751,"uid":21028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T14:22:20.000Z","msg":"同二世祖打工係最好"},{"pid":"71d97b928519c5f6785744a2e825ec2c30ee7ddf","tid":1394751,"uid":258362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T14:28:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n「救人！」世紀最大一人一Email 夾公務員罷工行動 第二波<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1394757\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1394757</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}